<br />\n但當大部分人都係咁時<br />\n而你永遠唔知其他人條線高定低<br />\n你唔偽善就變左你無禮貌<br />\n所以結論係禮多人不怪<br />\n偽善點都好過俾人話無禮貌<br />\n有理無理做左先唔好比位人入"},{"pid":"da62b7fb83eebfd61b844181959c27d21d33e46c","tid":1791740,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af5f9eb427b3404ee2f1e58456fcb84c53b2462","tid":1791740,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fe722ca5d35748217421125b3148313af88cda","tid":1791740,"uid":42910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d4dfb96644b19a855193c4124ed6cf57835ba7","tid":1791740,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"其實係一個好好探討既問題<br />\n好多野都係一線之差 包括我個問題<br />\n但往往無人比到一個好確實既答案點分條界線"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"真心相愛同係咪佔有慾作祟都係一個好問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"偽命題，依個世界唔存在真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nProblem solved"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"點會冇，我阿媽好愛我我好愛媽媽"},{"pid":"8fbef534f556f47cb8502681d38b487e372e8d42","tid":1791740,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da62b7fb83eebfd61b844181959c27d21d33e46c","tid":1791740,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af5f9eb427b3404ee2f1e58456fcb84c53b2462","tid":1791740,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fe722ca5d35748217421125b3148313af88cda","tid":1791740,"uid":42910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"真心相愛同係咪佔有慾作祟都係一個好問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"偽命題，依個世界唔存在真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nProblem solved"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"點會冇，我阿媽好愛我我好愛媽媽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"我諗佢講嘅愛係兩性/同性間嘅情愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a099f67201cd870598a09c22c6dda0640277754f","tid":1791740,"uid":30